  "opening_lines": [
    {
      "line": 1,
      "text": "TOOLS & IDEAS"
    },
    {
      "line": 4,
      "text": "Real Abuse"
    },
    {
      "line": 5,
      "text": "False Memory"
    },
    {
      "line": 12,
      "text": "We have many readers. They just don’t know it yet."
    },
    {
      "line": 13,
      "text": "You're going to help us find them."
    },
    {
      "line": 16,
      "text": "As Sonny Barger once said of the Hell’s Angels:"
    },
    {
      "line": 19,
      "text": "“We don’t:recru"
    },
    {
      "line": 22,
      "text": "O YOU KNOW"
    },
    {
      "line": 24,
      "text": "D someone who ought"
    },
    {
      "line": 25,
      "text": "to read a copy of"
    },
    {
      "line": 27,
      "text": "Whole Earth Review? A co-worker,"
    },
    {
      "line": 28,
      "text": "friend, daughter, father, neigh-"
    },
    {
      "line": 29,
      "text": "bor? People who smile rather"
    },
    {
      "line": 30,
      "text": "than bristle when their assump-"
    },
    {
      "line": 31,
      "text": "tions are challenged? People who"
    },
    {
      "line": 32,
      "text": "want something more nutritious"
    },
    {
      "line": 33,
      "text": "than sound bites? People who"
    },
    {
      "line": 34,
      "text": "might not follow this season’s"
    },
    {
      "line": 35,
      "text": "fashion trend, but who are inter-"
    },
    {
      "line": 36,
      "text": "ested in the tool or idea that will"
    },
    {
      "line": 37,
      "text": "be important next year, or the"
    },
    {
      "line": 38,
      "text": "year after next? Do you know"
    },
    {
      "line": 39,
      "text": "several such people? If you"
    },
    {
      "line": 40,
      "text": "do, we’re halfway home."
    },
    {
      "line": 43,
      "text": "You know what WER has to"
    },
    {
      "line": 44,
      "text": "offer, and you know why you"
    },
    {
      "line": 45,
      "text": "are one of the people who find"
    },
    {
      "line": 46,
      "text": "our quarterly bundle of mind-"
    },
    {
      "line": 47,
      "text": "stretchers and life-enhancers"
    },
    {
      "line": 48,
      "text": "so valuable."
    },
    {
      "line": 51,
      "text": "If you are willing to hand-deliver"
    },
    {
      "line": 52,
      "text": "them to potential subscribers, ask"
    },
    {
      "line": 53,
      "text": "us for copies of the latest issue."
    },
    {
      "line": 54,
      "text": "We'll mail them to you. You give"
    },
    {
      "line": 55,
      "text": "them to people who might sub-"
    },
    {
      "line": 56,
      "text": "scribe. We also have these really"
    },
    {
      "line": 57,
      "text": "cool baseball-type cards that"
    },
    {
      "line": 59,
      "text": "you can hand out."
    },
    {
      "line": 62,
      "text": "Whole Earth is ready for the"
    },
    {
      "line": 63,
